title: Prohibits peace officers from inquiring about the nationality or immigration status of a victim or witness to a criminal offense
summary: Prohibits law enforcement agencies or peace officers from inquiring about the nationality or immigration status of a victim or witness to a criminal offense.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the criminal procedure law, in relation to prohibiting law enforcement agencies and peace officers from inquiring about the nationality or immigration status of a victim or witness to a criminal offense
